My asthma's gone!
Listen to me breathe.

237
00:13:51,463 --> 00:13:55,593
<i>From that moment on,
my life as I knew it was over.</i>

238
00:13:55,701 --> 00:13:58,261
Only one member of the Springfield Seven
was identified.

239
00:13:58,370 --> 00:14:00,702
She's been described
as a woman in her early 30s...

240
00:14:00,806 --> 00:14:04,003
yellow complexion
and may be extremely helpful.

241
00:14:04,109 --> 00:14:07,044
<i>For Channel 6 News,
I'm Kenny Brockelstein.</i>

242
00:14:07,146 --> 00:14:09,046
Homer.

243
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:16,620
I'll miss you, Homer.

244
