Don't you want to play
"good cop, bad cop"?

321
00:18:54,633 --> 00:18:58,330
- Ma'am, we're all good cops.
- I had no intention of playing the good cop.

322
00:18:59,771 --> 00:19:02,171
Look, we know
you bought the tombstone.

323
00:19:02,274 --> 00:19:06,506
We know the fugitive visited that tombstone.
Whose tombstone was it?

324
00:19:06,612 --> 00:19:08,671
Just lift up
your coffee cups and see.

325
00:19:11,183 --> 00:19:13,743
- Good lord!
- Put out an A.P. B...

326
00:19:13,852 --> 00:19:17,015
