329
00:19:21,827 --> 00:19:23,988
Uh, cancel that A.P.B.

330
00:19:24,096 --> 00:19:26,656
But, uh- Oh, bring back
some of them, uh, gyros.

331
00:19:26,765 --> 00:19:29,825
Uh, Chief, you're
talking into your wallet.

332
00:19:29,935 --> 00:19:32,904
Grandma, have you ever thought
about moving back to Springfield?

333
00:19:33,005 --> 00:19:35,530
You could live with Grampa again.

334
00:19:39,578 --> 00:19:42,206
Oh, I'm a living joke.

335
00:19:42,314 --> 00:19:44,214
You know, Lisa...

336
00:19:44,316 --> 00:19:46,978
<i>it might be nice to rest for a while.</i>

337
00:19:47,085 --> 00:19:49,952
<i>Mom, there's nothing
to be alarmed about.</i>

338
00:19:50,055 --> 00:19:53,047
But could you take one last look
at the family and join me in the kitchen?

339
00:19:55,427 --> 00:19:59,989
I've been waiting
25 years for this moment.

340
00:20:03,168 --> 00:20:05,068
<i>Huh?</i>

341
