I'm sorry, sir.
I must've taped over that.

342
00:20:15,948 --> 00:20:18,508
Freeze! F.B.I.
The jig is up.

343
00:20:18,617 --> 00:20:21,677
All right, I admit it.
I am the Lindbergh baby.

344
00:20:21,787 --> 00:20:25,279
Waah! Waah! Goo, goo.
I miss my fly-fly dada.

345
00:20:25,390 --> 00:20:27,358
Are you trying to stall us,
or are you just senile?

346
00:20:27,459 --> 00:20:30,292
A little from column "A,"
a little from column "B."

347
00:20:30,395 --> 00:20:32,795
Sir, she's gone!

348
00:20:37,603 --> 00:20:41,596
- We made it, Homer!
- It's all thanks to our anonymous tipster.

349
00:20:41,707 --> 00:20:44,642
But who are you?
