350
00:20:44,743 --> 00:20:48,110
Well, it's 'cause of your old lady
that I got rid of the asthma...

351
00:20:48,213 --> 00:20:50,443
- that was keeping me out of the academy.
- Thanks.

352
00:20:50,549 --> 00:20:53,074
Sure. Just think of me
as an anonymous friend...

