358
00:21:07,499 --> 00:21:10,957
At least this time
I'm awake for your good-bye.

359
00:21:11,069 --> 00:21:12,866
Oh, Homer.

360
00:21:12,971 --> 00:21:16,964
Remember, whatever happens,
you have a mother...

361
00:21:17,075 --> 00:21:19,441
